snippet.textDisplay:
Did you ever hear the tragedy of Chef Mike the Wise?


I thought not. It's not a story restaurants owners would tell you.


It's a Kitchen Nightmares legend.




Chef Mike was an all purpose Lord of the Kitchen, so powerful and so wise he could use its waves to influence the food to cook... He had such a knowledge of the culinary side that he could even keep the ones he cared about from overcooking. The culinary side of the Force is a pathway to many abilities some consider to be unnatural. He became so powerful... the only thing he was afraid of was losing his power, which eventually, of course, he did. Unfortunately, he taught his apprentices everything he knew, then his apprentice, named Ramsay, killed him in his sleep. hmm ironic he could save others from debt, but not himself.
